Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:09.81,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:14.28,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.28,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:20.62,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.54,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:29.46,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.26,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:41.18,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:43.85,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:48.35,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:52.07,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.86,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:59.74,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.58,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:11.84,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.92,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.72,apollon op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
