Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:52.38,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And having to hike up this hill from now on, just to get to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It all makes me want to throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.40,sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs60\shad0\bord0\fnEraserDust\b0\blur0.75\c&HF3F8D8&\pos(280,161)}Nishimi Kaoru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.82,sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs50\shad0\bord0\fnEraserDust\b0\blur0.85\c&H48513C&\frz24.533\frx2\fry316\pos(1103,81)\org(1176,72)}Nishimi Kaoru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:16.90,sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs10\shad0\bord0\fnEraserDust\b0\blur0.85\c&HF3F8D8&\pos(628,364)}Nishimi Kaoru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:10.40,apollon main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Joining us today is Nishimi Kaoru, all the way from Yokosuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:14.69,apollon main,Teacher,0,0,0,,{It seems}He was at the top of the \Nclass at his previous school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.90,apollon main,Teacher,0,0,0,,I hope you all will study just as hard as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.82,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm Nishimi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:20.82,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,{\a6}Yokosuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:21.99,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,{\a6}Isn't that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm used to this routine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:24.83,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,{\a6}What a nerd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.04,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,{\a6}Spoiled rich kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:27.83,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Their unreserved stares...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Their Kyushu dialect that I can't follow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.80,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This is my most memorable welcome yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.39,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Nishimi. Nishimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.81,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Have you decided what club you're gonna join?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.27,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Are you interested in radios?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.73,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Look at that loser, Maruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.69,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Two four-eyed bookworm runts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.36,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,They're made for each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.86,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.53,apollon main,,0,0,0,,They picked on you because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:08.25,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Infantile creeps like that can't do \Nanything unless they're in a pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.09,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Nishimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.59,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in radios either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.09,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Nishimi, one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:27.31,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't annoy\Nthe guy who sits behind me. {orig: It's not a good idea to antagonize \Nthe guy who sits behind me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.81,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,He's a notorious thug. Not even\Nthe teacher can deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:35.57,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,His name is Kawabuchi, and if he starts targeting you, you're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Just thinking about it is nauseating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.24,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Nishimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.41,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Nishimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.91,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm Mukae Ritsuko, the class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:55.33,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to show you around \Nthe school during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.00,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.92,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't feel sick anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.60,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,The gym is back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:17.61,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And the nurse's office is in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.15,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay, Nishimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.78,apollon main,Ritsuo,0,0,0,,Be careful! {orig: Whatcha think you're doin'?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.16,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Whoops! It just slipped out of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.16,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.53,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.16,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.16,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Never saw him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:36.17,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, Mukae, how do I get to the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:42.67,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I've moved from school to school \Never since first grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:42.63,apollon main,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fad(200,0)\shad0\bord0\fnEraserDust\b0\blur1.5\pos(879,248)\c&HBFA984&}Nishimi Kaoru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:47.80,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If something unexpected happened, \NI would lose my sense of equilibrium,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.14,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,and even minor stress would trigger my nausea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:56.65,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But eventually, I found a place at school \Nwhere I could regain my bearings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right. If I can \Njust get to the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.45,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.34,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You've finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:26.30,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,come for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.31,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:36.27,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Why you holdin' my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.10,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0}{\fscx120} {\r}the one who grabbed {\i1}my{\i0}{\fscx120} {\r}hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:43.36,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I get it. You must be the key thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.40,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,In that case, I ain't holdin' back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.20,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Are you Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.62,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Is this what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.62,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Then you goons are the thieves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.46,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,The roof belongs to us senior smokers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.59,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.76,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I want the key to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.43,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,A candyass like you has no\Nbusiness being up here! {orig: A candyass like you better \Nget the hell outta here!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.10,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You want it that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.90,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I-I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:21.73,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hold on to this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.44,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.69,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:12.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How reckless can you be?\N Going up against three seniors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.29,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,This is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.21,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I can really have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.21,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.29,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,For 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:30.13,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you thought I'd hand it over for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.80,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I put my ass on the line to get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.10,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,100,000 is cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:35.85,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.06,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:41.39,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I didn't even go to class once today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:49.86,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,City boy like that's got no common \Nground with us country boys.{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.36,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I can't believe you, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.91,apollon main,,0,0,0,,You got in {\i1}another{\i0}{\fscx140} {\r}fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.16,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,It's just some scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.04,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,You... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.71,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko, who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:10.05,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna answer a guy \Nwho does nothin' but fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Maruo! Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:18.10,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,Th-That's Nishimi Kaoru, a new transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:21.43,apollon main,Maruo,0,0,0,,He's supposed to be rich and a real brainiac.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.52,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.86,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Later, Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.99,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hi there, rich boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.28,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,From now on, your name is "Richie."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.99,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Let's me and you be pals, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.20,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,Sentaro's got a new target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.62,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,It's curtains for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.29,apollon main,Student,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.66,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I feel sick again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.13,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry. I've got a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.50,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:52.84,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I can't pay 100,000, but could you \Nlend me the key just this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.22,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.30,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,But it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.85,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey! It's raining outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.27,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll be fine if I take an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:09.15,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,It sounds like fun! I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:18.91,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What the hell? This ain't much fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:22.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Of course not. I'm not up here to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:23.87,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Then why come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.92,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If you're bored, you can always go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:28.58,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.96,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Class ain't my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.54,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Quit following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.34,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,This feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.72,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, take a shower with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.06,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.73,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:31.23,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Nothin' good's ever come out of bein' scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.15,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Let yourself get a little wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.41,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.95,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:46.50,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.83,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You never stop causing me trouble.{this sounds terrible}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.79,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,We're going right to the nurse's office so you can borrow a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:55.38,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I'll get your gym clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.96,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'll meet you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:16.28,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is that jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.45,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What, you can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.33,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, sort of. I play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.54,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Classical, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.00,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Classical, huh? What a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:31.83,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.84,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.34,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Looks like she's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:42.68,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I didn't notice with your glasses on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.35,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,but you have a really \Npretty face, Nishimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.97,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:50.31,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, is it rude to call a man \N"pretty"? I meant "handsome."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.35,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.19,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.24,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm a human hair dryer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.15,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.24,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,There he goes again, bein' scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.12,apollon main,,0,0,0,,What a fraidy cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.58,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.58,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.96,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How could I be scared anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:19.13,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,After all... that rain felt way\Nbetter than I could've imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.84,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:30.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Even with everyone staring at \Nme, I can breathe normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.98,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What kind of magic is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's great, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:47.37,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You can play the piano, even\Nthough you're a sailor? {orig: Being able to play the \Npiano, even being a sailor?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:53.41,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Kaoru, I'm going away again for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.87,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Be a good boy while I'm gone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.88,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,When I play the piano,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:02.13,apollon main,,0,0,0,,I can forget about the loneliness caused by Dad being away and the rest of the bad stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.47,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:09.31,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Your uncle in Kyushu has a huge grand piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.48,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Dad... I don't want a grand piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.60,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What I want is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.33,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.70,apollon main,,0,0,0,,You're up really early this morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.21,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,You wanna play the piano? Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:39.00,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,Mariko feels like hearing \Na tune that'll wake her up.{I hate using third person but w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.84,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But playing this early would—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.51,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,I wanna hear it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:48.01,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,Mariko will take responsibility, so please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.60,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.16,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.96,apollon main,Aunt,0,0,0,,Excuse me? What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:22.46,apollon main,Aunt,0,0,0,,Playing the piano at this hour... \NDon't you have any sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.26,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Aunt. Mariko wanted—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:29.01,apollon main,Mariko,0,0,0,,See? This is why I told you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:32.10,apollon main,Aunt,0,0,0,,Putting the blame on someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.56,apollon main,Aunt,0,0,0,,I guess it's difficult for a \Nfather to raise a child alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:42.44,apollon main,Aunt,0,0,0,,Although, it's your {\i1}mother{\i0\fscx130} {\fscx100}who's responsible for abandoning the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.48,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Nishimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Mukae?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.57,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro didn't come today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.99,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Are you lonely without him around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.50,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry. I wasn't able to \Ncomprehend that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.96,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll be quite pleased if he \Nsees fit to extend his absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:06.38,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I-I see. It looked to me like \Nyou two were hitting it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:14.18,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Everyone else is afraid of Sentaro, \Nbut you act normally in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.73,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I bet you and Sentaro could become buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Mukae...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.02,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Give me a break. That smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:27.36,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I mean it. As his childhood \Nfriend, I can guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:33.20,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Childhood friend? So that's why you're \Nso casual with each other's names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:37.41,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, you can call me\Nby my first name too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:42.25,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And then maybe I'll call you "Kaoru."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.54,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, Kaoru, Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:47.55,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this echo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.22,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sorry, I said that without \Nasking. If you don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.05,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, it's fine! I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Ri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.18,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:01.69,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Do you know of any record shops in town that sell classical music?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.73,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Records? We've got tons \Nof them at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.98,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You should come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:12.82,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You understand what I really mean,\Ndon't you... Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:15.91,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I-I think things are moving a little too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.41,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is this how Kyushu girls behave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.54,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This is our shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.54,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And this is my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.71,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Fath—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.51,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,M-My name is Nishimi Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.63,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Your daughter has been very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.68,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,The classical section is right here, Kaoru. {orig: The classical section is over\Non that shelf, Kaoru.   - but then he starts browsing right in front of them}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.77,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.77,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What kind of records are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.81,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, mainly piano pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.32,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I play the piano myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.69,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.15,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.11,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.87,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Ritsuko! Outsiders aren't allowed down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:03.29,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Dad, Kaoru is a good \Nfriend of mine and Sentaro's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.79,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Sen's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:08.00,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, I'm not his friend, just—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.29,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.38,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.22,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.53,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.87,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Th-That's what I want to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.04,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko! We got an intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.54,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Listen to this, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.04,apollon main,,0,0,0,,Kaoru says he can play the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.13,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.17,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I'll bet you anything it's just \Nclassical rich kid crap, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.51,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Jazz is the only music for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:37.01,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru. Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.64,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Hey, Kaoru, have a try at the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.64,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:45.72,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko, only jazz is allowed in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.06,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,If it's the piano you want to hear, I'll play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.37,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, I know this piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.79,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I can't take it any more. It's like {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.96,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Wrong! That ain't even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:18.63,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? \NI played it exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.13,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,I couldn't feel any swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:24.01,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,If you play it without feelin' it, \Nit don't sound like no {\i1}jazz{\i0}{\fscx120} {\r}to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:28.39,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You know what? I'd love to hear you two do a session together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.39,apollon main,Kaoru & Sen,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.60,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Nah, Ri'ko. That's a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:36.82,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,This guy don't get jazz, and\N he's got no sense for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:40.11,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,A little practice and \Nplaying that'll be a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.12,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.75,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, Kaoru! Come back again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.59,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ri, do you know the name\Nof the piano piece he played?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.97,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:03.14,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,The only thing Sen can play on \Nthe piano is the intro to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:08.35,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Art Blakey and the Jazz \NMessengers' {\i1}Moanin'{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.44,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'd like this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:20.90,apollon main,Dad,0,0,0,,Wasn't he here to buy classical music?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.61,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.70,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't know why,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:36.54,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but his drums just wouldn't \Nstop thundering in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.67,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.13,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:45.51,apollon main,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Aren't you walking strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.55,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Really? This is how I always walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.64,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.27,apollon main,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko! Richie! See ya's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:04.45,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're running down the hill that \NI hate so much like it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:09.24,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What can you see beyond it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:15.08,apollon main,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is it a view that I've never seen before?
